            "varname": "ups_nut_critical_charge",
            "caption": "Ups Nut: Critical Charge",
            "description": "CRIT threshold for battery charge in percent. When omitted, the plugin prefers the UPS-reported `battery.charge.low` (which is the level at which the UPS itself triggers the LB flag). Falls back to '10:' if neither the UPS nor the admin configured a value. Supports Nagios ranges.",
